<subSubSection pageId="24" pageNumber="109" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="24.[136,1452,986,1805]" pageId="24" pageNumber="109">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[189,328,1382,1408]" pageId="24" pageNumber="109">Etymology:</emphasis>
—The specific epithet commemorates the Dutch botanist Henriette Dorothea Schotsman (1921– 2004), who greatly contributed to taxonomic knowledge of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="von Linne" authorityYear="1753" box="[804,925,1418,1444]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Plantaginaceae" genus="Callitriche" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="24" pageNumber="109" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[804,925,1418,1444]" italics="true" pageId="24" pageNumber="109">Callitriche</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="24.[136,1452,986,1805]" pageId="24" pageNumber="109">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[189,265,1454,1480]" pageId="24" pageNumber="109">Notes:</emphasis>
— 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Lansdown &amp; Hassemer" authorityYear="2021" box="[294,592,1454,1480]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Plantaginaceae" genus="Callitriche" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="24" pageNumber="109" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="schotsmaniana">
<emphasis box="[294,592,1454,1480]" italics="true" pageId="24" pageNumber="109">Callitriche schotsmaniana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is known only from two gatherings from the same area and it is likely that these do not include representation of the full range of variation. The fruit appear to be unique within the genus in having a thicker central area surrounded by a thinner zone which would equate to the wing in most species, but there is no structural differentiation within this thinner area. This could be affected by the preservation process and more material is needed to enable better description of the fruit.There is a need for more survey and data collection from the area in which the collections were made.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="24.[136,1452,986,1805]" pageId="24" pageNumber="109">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[189,435,1670,1696]" pageId="24" pageNumber="109">Conservation status:</emphasis>
—Available information is inadequate to derive an informed assessment of the conservation status of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Lansdown &amp; Hassemer" authorityYear="2021" box="[237,438,1706,1733]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Plantaginaceae" genus="Callitriche" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="24" pageNumber="109" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="schotsmaniana">
<emphasis box="[237,438,1706,1733]" italics="true" pageId="24" pageNumber="109">C. schotsmaniana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and it is therefore classed as Data Deficient (DD).
</paragraph>
